Purely Automatic.
Two clutches in the hub one actuating- the driving
& the other the brake.
The brake is applied by a band to a drum on the
hub.& can be put on at any part of the stroke.
Rider can mount& dismount asusual.
The weight is only a few ounces heavier than
the ordinary hub.
Efficiency& workmanship of the highest Order.
